# Implementation Plan - Canvas AI (NextStep v3.0)

This plan outlines the steps to build the "Canvas AI" application, a visual orchestration OS powered by the Microsoft Agent Framework.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a greenfield implementation. We are creating the `src` directory from scratch.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend (Python / Microsoft Agent Framework)
#### [NEW] [backend/main.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver3/src/backend/main.py)
- **Goal**: FastAPI entry point.
- **Details**: Expose WebSocket endpoint `/ws` for real-time agent streaming.

#### [NEW] [backend/orchestrator.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver3/src/backend/orchestrator.py)
- **Goal**: Wrap `agent-framework`.
- **Details**: Implement `MagenticBuilder` to create a manager, researcher, and coder agent swarm. Handle `MagenticBuilder.run_stream()` and broadcast events to WebSocket.

#### [NEW] [backend/agents.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver3/src/backend/agents.py)
- **Goal**: Define specific ChatAgents (Architect, Critic).
- **Details**: Configure specific system instructions and tools (if any).

### Frontend (Next.js / React Flow)
#### [NEW] [frontend/package.json](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver3/src/frontend/package.json)
- **Goal**: Project manifesto.
- **Details**: Next.js, React Flow, TailwindCSS, Lucide React, Framer Motion.

#### [NEW] [frontend/app/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver3/src/frontend/app/page.tsx)
- **Goal**: Main Canvas Interface.
- **Details**: Full-screen React Flow instance.

#### [NEW] [frontend/components/OrchestratorPanel.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver3/src/frontend/components/OrchestratorPanel.tsx)
- **Goal**: The "Cockpit".
- **Details**: Glassmorphism panel showing the Chat Stream and Active Agent indicators (as per inspiration image).

#### [NEW] [frontend/components/nodes/InputNode.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver3/src/frontend/components/nodes/InputNode.tsx)
- **Goal**: Rich media card.
- **Details**: Displays file icon, name, and metadata.

#### [NEW] [frontend/components/nodes/AgentNode.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nextstep-ver3/src/frontend/components/nodes/AgentNode.tsx)
- **Goal**: Visualizing the agent process.
- **Details**: Animated node showing "Thinking" state.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- **Backend**: Run `pytest` on `backend/tests` (will create basic smoke tests).
- **Frontend**: Run `npm run build` to verify type safety.

### Manual Verification
1.  **Start Backend**: `uvicorn src.backend.main:app --reload`
2.  **Start Frontend**: `npm run dev`
3.  **Action**: Open `localhost:3000`.
4.  **Test**: Click "Start Workflow" (mock or real).
5.  **Verify**:
    -   Orchestrator Panel appears.
    -   "Architect" and "Critic" agents appear in the stream.
    -   React Flow canvas updates with new nodes.
